results.deck: A science fiction franchise of isolation and fear as Ellen Ripley survives against aliens.
results.description:
Alien Films

Main Series

1979 - Alien, directed by Ridley Scott
1986 - Aliens, directed by James Cameron
1992 - Alien 3, directed by David Fincher
1997 - Alien: Resurrection , directed by Jean-Pierre Jeunet

Crossover Films

2004 - Alien vs. Predator, directed by Paul W.S. Anderson
2007 - Alien vs. Predator: Requiem, directed by Colin & Greg Strause
